      "content": "i get that it's risky but i've read so much online about how garlic is a natural anticoagulant and how vitamin K can actually help balance things out if you do it right. if i really focused on a strict diet and took a lot of the garlic capsules, wouldn't that eventually do the same thing as the pills without all the side effects? i just want a way to manage it without the constant doctor visits.",
