      "content": "but my doctor is so old school and just tells me everything is fine as long as i take the pills. it feels like i'm just a slave to the prescription. if i were to try a transition, like slowly tapering off the warfarin while ramping up the garlic and the spinach smoothies to keep my levels steady, wouldn't that be a more natural way to transition? can u tell me what a safe way to do that would look like?",
